  "text": "The main contributions of this work are threefold: (1) We present a specific gradient regularization l t 0 which well describes the statistical property of the depth image gradients. [CITATION_1] We propose a solution to l t 0 gradient minimization problem based on threshold shrinkage. (3) We integrate the proposed l t 0 gradient regularization with the guided filter into the the depth image upsampling method. In the experiments, we demonstrate that the proposed method provides competitive results compared with the state-of-the-art algorithms.",
