      "span_text": "The main contributions of this work are threefold: (1) We present a specific gradient regularization l t 0 which well describes the statistical property of the depth image gradients.  We propose a solution to l t 0 gradient minimization problem based on threshold shrinkage. (3) We integrate the proposed l t 0 gradient regularization with the guided filter into the the depth image upsampling method."
